The Telegram contest for JavaScript developers is starting today. 

Total prize fund: $200,000.  
Dates: Nov 3 - Nov 17.
Goal: Create a simplified web version of Telegram.

Details: https://t.me/contest/118

üíé Switzerland-based firm Gram Vault is set to become the first major seller of the GRAM cryptocurrency.

Given the price of GRAM is $3 apiece, the total amount of assets stored may be standing at $3 billion.

Gram Vault provides services to TON investors, ensures the connection with top exchanges, and positions itself as a primary GRAM storage solution for early investors of the Telegram Open Network.

The company has bank accounts in Switzerland, Lichtenstein, and the U.S.

For more detail, view the survey attached below that has been recently e-mailed to some of the early investors.

The latest update brings scheduled messages, better themes and more privacy for those who need it most.

Holding down the send button now gives the option to schedule a message. Choose the date and time, and let Telegram take care of the delivery. Set a reminder for yourself by scheduling something in your Saved Messages.

Cloud Themes allow you to create a unique combination of theme, wallpaper and accent color to quickly share across platforms and update for all who use it.

Keeping your phone number confidential has become more universal with the new setting Who Can Find Me By My Number. This additional layer of privacy prevents even people who add your contact information to their device from being able to match your profile to your number.
